{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The repo already has session, catalog, workflow, and chat plumbing in place, so I\u2019m threading genre selection into those existing seams rather than inventing a parallel path. I hit one dead end immediately: the skill lives in the global...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_5", "text": "The repo already has session, catalog, workflow, and chat plumbing in place, so I\u2019m threading genre selection into those existing seams rather than inventing a parallel path. I hit one dead end immediately: the skill lives in the global Codex skills directory, not under this repo, so I\u2019m loading it from there and then mapping it onto the current app.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 13, "prompt_index": 41, "prompt_name": "40 \u2014 Genre Selection API and UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T18:30:25-07:00"}
