{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve decided to keep the catalog endpoint backed by the seeded database rows instead of bypassing the existing catalog model with raw YAML reads. That keeps the UI contract aligned with the same durable reference data the session selecti...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_67", "text": "I\u2019ve decided to keep the catalog endpoint backed by the seeded database rows instead of bypassing the existing catalog model with raw YAML reads. That keeps the UI contract aligned with the same durable reference data the session selection uses, and I can seed the compose database explicitly during verification so the rendered app exercises the real path.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 132, "prompt_index": 41, "prompt_name": "40 \u2014 Genre Selection API and UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T18:34:23-07:00"}
