{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \"curl -sv 'http://127.0.0.1:8565/api/v1/catalog/genres' >/tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.out 2>/tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.err && cat /tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.out && echo '---ERR---' && cat /tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.err\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "[{\"id\":\"de8e8f67-289a-4555-88ee-bcae4fdc172e\",\"slug\":\"quest-fantasy\",\"label\":\"Quest Fantasy\",\"description\":\"A bedtime-safe adventure with a clear destination, gentle bravery, and a warm return home.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Keep the journey wondrous rather than perilous; any danger should feel temporary, buffered by helpers, and resolved before sleep.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Leave a familiar safe place, face one meaningful but gentle challenge, and return more settled and confident.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Low to moderate; suspense should come from uncertainty, not threat.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"The final image should land in shelter, reunion, or visible rest.\"},\"sort_order\":0},{\"id\":\"79f1996e-7e49-4679-a5f9-5ac89f4d452f\",\"slug\":\"gentle-mystery\",\"label\":\"Gentle Mystery\",\"description\":\"A puzzle-forward bedtime story driven by clues, curiosity, and a reassuring explanation.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Mystery should never feel menacing; clues can be strange, but the world must stay emotionally safe and readable.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Notice a small mystery, gather clues, make a calm discovery, and restore ease.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Low; suspense comes from curiosity and anticipation rather than fear.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"The reveal should repair uncertainty and make the world feel kinder than before.\"},\"sort_order\":1},{\"id\":\"7e2e2b97-25e4-431e-bff9-23ecd726c14d\",\"slug\":\"cozy-animal-adventure\",\"label\":\"Cozy Animal Adventure\",\"description\":\"Animal characters roam, explore, and solve small problems in a world built for comfort and wonder.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Keep animal-scale stakes manageable and end with nesting, denning, or other visible signs of safety.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Venture a short distance from comfort, learn something sweet or useful, and return to a cozy habitat.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Low; physical risk should be implied lightly and quickly soothed.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"The ending should emphasize home, family, and rhythmic natural quiet.\"},\"sort_order\":2},{\"id\":\"75058248-edd8-4b54-8908-98638979e115\",\"slug\":\"magical-friendship\",\"label\":\"Magical Friendship\",\"description\":\"Relationship-first stories where enchantment supports connection, trust, and emotional repair.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Keep interpersonal conflict mild, repair visible, and magic supportive instead of chaotic.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Meet or reconnect, navigate a gentle emotional misunderstanding, and deepen the bond through care.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Low; the heart of the story is vulnerability, not peril.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"End with closeness, belonging, and a felt sense of mutual care.\"},\"sort_order\":3},{\"id\":\"d2309e38-3b41-48b5-96da-5b3c55ee6c48\",\"slug\":\"dreamworld-voyage\",\"label\":\"Dreamworld Voyage\",\"description\":\"Drifting, surreal adventures that feel secure, beautiful, and intentionally sleepy.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Even when dream logic gets strange, maintain orientation through comforting guides, repeated motifs, and gentle landings.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Drift into an unusual realm, explore a few dreamlike images, and descend into deeper calm.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Very low; dream shifts should feel curious, not destabilizing.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"The ending should feel like a soft arrival into sleep itself.\"},\"sort_order\":4},{\"id\":\"737ae90b-8493-4342-ac61-821660998791\",\"slug\":\"soft-science-wonder\",\"label\":\"Soft Science Wonder\",\"description\":\"Science-flavored bedtime stories driven by curiosity, observation, and awe rather than technical complexity.\",\"bedtime_safety_notes\":\"Keep scientific concepts accessible, reassuring, and emotionally warm; discovery should never become sterile or high-pressure.\",\"arc_notes\":{\"core_arc\":\"Notice a natural or cosmic question, explore it with gentle experimentation, and end with bigger wonder plus calm understanding.\",\"tension_ceiling\":\"Low; the challenge should be intellectual or practical, not dangerous.\",\"bedtime_payoff\":\"The world feels larger, kinder, and more connected by the end.\"},\"sort_order\":5}]---ERR---\n*   Trying 127.0.0.1:8565...\n* Connected to 127.0.0.1 (127.0.0.1) port 8565\n> GET /api/v1/catalog/genres HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 127.0.0.1:8565\r\n> User-Agent: curl/8.7.1\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Request completely sent off\n< HTTP/1.1 200 OK\r\n< date: Thu, 02 Apr 2026 01:48:36 GMT\r\n< server: uvicorn\r\n< content-length: 4001\r\n< content-type: application/json\r\n< \r\n{ [4001 bytes data]\n* Connection #0 to host 127.0.0.1 left intact\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"curl -sv 'http://127.0.0.1:8565/api/v1/catalog/genres' >/tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.out 2>/tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.err && cat /tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.out && echo '---ERR---' && cat /tmp/storyteller-catalog-host.err\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_176", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 335, "prompt_index": 41, "prompt_name": "40 \u2014 Genre Selection API and UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T18:48:36-07:00"}
