{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 40 end to end and wrote the required reviewer summary at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/40_genre_selection_api_and_ui/summary.md). The main work lande...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_304", "text": "Implemented prompt 40 end to end and wrote the required reviewer summary at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/40_genre_selection_api_and_ui/summary.md).\n\nThe main work landed in `47f1fa4` and a browser-found follow-up fix landed in `de4115e`. Backend now serves the genre catalog and persists genre selection durably; frontend now renders the curated genre stage, saves the selection, echoes it into chat/history, and previews the tone step. Live browser QA exposed a real contract bug in the selection POST body, and that was fixed before closeout.\n\nVerification completed:\n- Backend: targeted prompt-40 tests passed, then `backend/tests` passed (`110 passed, 5 skipped`) and `ruff check` passed.\n- Frontend: targeted `SessionWorkspacePage` tests passed after the fix (`11 passed`), full frontend tests passed (`54 passed`), `lint` passed, and `build` passed.\n- Browser QA: captured and reviewed [desktop before](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-40-genre-desktop-before.png), [desktop after](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-40-genre-desktop-after.png), and [mobile genre card](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-40-genre-mobile-before.png). The live desktop session advanced from `genre` to `tone` with `Quest Fantasy` persisted.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 563, "prompt_index": 41, "prompt_name": "40 \u2014 Genre Selection API and UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T19:04:12-07:00"}
